{"parentUuid":"01a05555-bd84-471b-9392-26160159dbe1","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"c899109a-85f0-4ce2-8d4b-537fc48bb9f2","agentId":"aa041f3ac0f60e829","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_RWXqxrClP1JAICC80zas0igm","type":"tool_result","content":"35:| Integration enumeration block in generate prompt | `prompts.py` | V1-D + V5-2 |\n214:    for i, (phase_id, phase_content, start_line) in enumerate(sections):\n276:    for i, m in enumerate(matches):\n528:    for i, line in enumerate(lines):\n585:            for j, rline in enumerate(roadmap_lines):\n598:                for j, rline in enumerate(roadmap_lines):\n1299:Before generating the roadmap phases, you MUST first enumerate ALL\n1325:- Import chains: adding import statements from consumer to producer\n1367:| X-002 | V1-D vs V5-2 overlapping prompt constraints | Merged into single `INTEGRATION_ENUMERATION_BLOCK`. V5-2's enumeration requirement is the base; V1-D's specific examples (dispatch tables, constructor injection, import chains, registration) are incorporated. |\n1373:| X-008 | V4-5 stateful registry vs stateless pipeline | V4-5 rejected. Architecturally incompatible with current stateless pipeline model. All other variants implicitly reject this approach. |\n1437:7. `prompts.py` -- add enumeration block + 6th fidelity dimension\n1448:| Obligation ledger + manifest injection (prevention layer via prompt state) | V2-B + V3-2 merged | After pipeline state management design approved; requires prompt injection testing |\n1497:| Obligation ledger + manifest injection | V2-B + V3-2 | Requires state management; deferred to Phase 2 |\n1498:| Requirement registry | V4-5 | Architecturally incompatible with stateless pipeline |\n\n[Showing results with pagination = limit: 120, offset: 0]"}]},"uuid":"172b0354-35e7-4fe4-8d72-1faa55a4c227","timestamp":"2026-03-17T18:48:37.267Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"01a05555-bd84-471b-9392-26160159dbe1","userType":"external","cwd":"/config/workspace/I